              <p class="card-text">Our company is a newly established <br>provider of innovative solutions and <br>services Founded in 2023 our mission <br>is to make a positive impact on <br>the world We are committed to <br>delivering exceptional value to our <br>customers and making a difference <br>in their lives.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="About-text">
