              <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-body-secondary">How We Started</h6>
              <p class="card-text">Our story began with a vision to <br>create a company that would make <br>a difference in the world Our <br>founders had a passion for innovation <br>and a desire to create a better <br>future We started the company with <br>a small team and a big dream <br>and we are excited to see what <br>the future holds.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="About-text" id="mission">
          <div class="card cards"data-aos="slide-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title mt-3">Our Mission</h5>
              <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-body-secondary">What Drives Us</h6>
              <p class="card-text">Kibatto Development Foundation boldly<br> works in order to evangelize, improve <br>child nutrition, care for the<br>earth and ultimately end<br>hunger and poverty in Nation.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="About-text" id="values">
          <div class="card cards"data-aos="slide-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title mt-3 px-3">Our Values</h5>
              <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-body-secondary px-3">What We Stand For</h6>
              <p class="card-text px-3">We believe in innovation teamwork <br>customer satisfaction integrity and <br>social responsibility These values guide <br>our decisions and actions and are <br>the foundation of our company culture <br>We strive to make a positive impact <br>on the world and make a difference <br>in the lives of our customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
